summary: Replace some Skyrim musics with Oblivion musics
descriptionHtml:
Oblivion Musics into Skyrim ! by AngelsTears

---------------------

DESCRIPTION :

This mod replace some musics of Skyrim with Oblivion musics. There\'s an optional file, in the \"OPTIONAL\" folder,
it\'s replace the main menu music with the main menu music of Oblivion.

---------------------

INSTALLATION :

Unzip the file you have downloaded, and place the \"music\" folder into the \"data\" folder of Skyrim.

---------------------

UN-INSTALLATION : 

Remove all the files you\'ve copied in the \"data\" folder of Skyrim.

---------------------

CREDITS :

Bethesda for created Skyrim, and Oblivion musics

---------------------

By AngelsTears, don\'t forget to endorse it if you like !
